description: The application can be used to lookup the price of Silver, Gold, and Bitcoin.  To use the app, say "Alexa, ask silverbug what's the price of Silver?"
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask silverbug what's the price of Silver?
Alexa, ask silverbug what's the current price of Bitcoin?
Alexa, ask silverbug what's the Gold price?
name: SilverBug
shortDescription: This application can be used to lookup the price of Silver, Gold, and Bitcoin.
